column34: 'BASE VAPE, HEATED TOBACCO REGULATIONS ON SCIENCE, NOT FICTION' A medical expert has urged the Food and Drug Administration (FDA) to base the proposed vape and heated tobacco regulations on science and not on fiction in the wake the beleaguered agency's admission that it received funding from foreign anti-tobacco organizations. PHILIPPINE STAR

column31: A medical expert has urged the Food and Drug Administration to base the proposed vape and heated tobacco regulations on science and not on fiction in the wake of the beleaguered agency’s admission that it received funding from foreign anti-tobacco organizations.
